<v Speaker 1>So we said that instead of saying literally the important thing, you can just use lo.

00:03:49.560 --> 00:03:58.120
<v Speaker 1>With any adjective and you get this idea of the important thing, lo importante, the important thing, lo increíble.

00:03:57.900 --> 00:03:59.420
